                    including home decor, jewelry, clothing, accessories, and much more. Each product is made with love and attention to detail, ensuring the
                    highest quality and authenticity.Join us in celebrating craftsmanship and supporting artisans around the world!
                </b>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <footer>
            <img src="~/images/khumalocraft - logo.png" alt="" />
            <h2>KhumaloCraft Emporium</h2>
            <p style="color: #f2f2f2">James Khumalo</p>
